des:
Open the skill and Alexa will automatically tell you how many days remain until all your upcoming events. Alexa can also remind you about the exact date.
Ask Alexa when Chouse Holidays are and she will give you a count down in days.
(NOT AFFILIATED WITH CHARTERHOUSE, MADE BY A PUPIL)
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
